  "自动同步：文件稳定 2 秒后上传到云端": "Auto Sync: Upload changes after 2s stability",
  "手动同步：点击同步按钮时上传": "Manual Sync: Upload changes when clicking sync button",
  "连接状态": "Connection Status",
  "绑定状态": "Binding Status",
  "微信扫码登录": "WeChat Scan Login",
  "新手使用引导": "Beginner Onboarding Guide",
  "欢迎使用": "Welcome",
  "它能够静默监控您指定的本地文件夹，捕获任何新建、修改、删除和重命名等文件变动事件，并能够安全地自动或手动同步到腾讯 IMA 个人知识库。在这里，我们将帮助您在本地常用编辑器与云端平台之间，架起一座可靠的双向同步桥梁。": "It monitors your local folders silently, captures file changes (created, modified, deleted, renamed), and syncs them automatically or manually to Tencent IMA. We bridge your local editors and the cloud.",
  "跳过": "Skip",
  "下一步": "Next",
  "上一步": "Back",
  "第一步：添加监控目录": "Step 1: Add Monitored Directory",
  "点击这里，选择你本地的文件夹。捕获到任何修改都会自动生成一条记录。": "Click here to select your local folder. Captured changes will auto-generate records.",
  "列表与树状模式": "List & Tree View Mode",
  "二级侧栏支持列表和树状视图切换，既能快速扫列表，也能按目录结构定位。": "The secondary sidebar supports toggling between list and tree views, letting you scan lists quickly or locate by folder structure.",
  "处理待同步": "Handle Pending",
  "左侧第二个入口集中展示未处理变动，可搜索路径、按类型筛选并批量处理。": "The second entry shows pending changes, supporting path search, type filtering, and bulk sync.",
  "最后配置云端和偏好": "Configure Cloud & Preferences",
  "让界面语言、外观以及开机自启等偏好设置保持可控。": "Control interface language, appearance, and auto launch settings.",
  "不再显示": "Don't show again",
