  "0个": "0个",
  "CSV / JSON 导出": "CSV/JSON Export",
  "FileSyncMonitor 将以开源方式提供。如果它帮你节省了时间，欢迎扫码捐赠支持后续维护。": "FileSyncMonitor will be available as open source. If it saves you time, you are welcome to scan the code to donate to support future maintenance.",
  "FileSyncMonitor 是一款面向 macOS 用户的轻量化文件夹自动监控与同步工具。": "FileSyncMonitor is a lightweight, automated folder monitoring and synchronization tool for macOS users.",
  "IMA 云端同步": "IMA Cloud Sync",
  "【免责声明】": "Disclaimer",
  "：本项目为非盈利开源项目。上述捐赠行为完全基于您的自愿，所得款项仅用于补贴开发者维护项目所产生的时间、网络与服务器等基本支出，捐赠并非此软件的牟利手段，且不代表任何商业化销售或服务承诺。我们不对本软件的同步效率、腾讯云端稳定性或任何由同步冲突导致的数据异常承诺任何商业保障 or 赔偿。请知悉！": ": This is a non-profit open-source project. Donations are entirely voluntary and are used only to offset the maintainer's time, network, server, and basic project costs. Donations are not a commercial sale or service commitment. We do not provide commercial guarantees or compensation for sync efficiency, Tencent cloud stability, or data issues caused by sync conflicts. Please be aware.",
  "仅在本地数据库标记为已同步，不上传/下载云端": "Only mark as synced on local database, not upload/download cloud",
  "从腾讯 IMA 知识库拉取云端变动到本地": "Take the cloud change from Tencent IMA Knowledge Base to on-premises",
  "从选择目录到过滤噪声文件，保证记录列表干净可用。": "From selecting directories to filtering noise files, keep your records list clean and available.",
  "作者: LancCJ (GitHub)": "By LancCJ (GitHub)",
