  "文件类型": "File Type",
  " 文件": " File",
  "该文件所属监控根目录暂未绑定腾讯 IMA 知识库，请前往系统设置完成绑定后才能执行同步。": "The monitored root folder for this file is not bound to a Tencent IMA knowledge base. Bind it in Settings before syncing.",
  "知识库绑定正常。随时可以开始单个文件的增量更新同步。": "Knowledge base binding is ready. You can sync this single file change at any time.",
  "包含待同步改动": "Pending Changes Included",
