  "统计报告": "Statistical reporting",
  "腾讯 IMA 账户登录": "Tencent IMA Login",
  "自动同步会在最后一次修改后重新等待 2 秒。": "Automatic sync will wait 2 seconds after the last modification.",
  "菜单栏图标会显示待同步数量，可快速打开窗口、标记完成或退出应用。": "The menu bar icon displays the number of syncs to be synced, allowing you to quickly open a window, mark it complete, or exit the app.",
