  "详情与快捷操作": "Details and shortcuts",
  "这是默认模式，适合确认后再同步。": "This is the default mode, suitable for confirmation and synchronization.",
  "退出程序": "Quit the program",
  "适合过滤编辑器临时文件和误操作，不会增加角标或通知。": "Suitable for filtering temporary files and mistakes in the editor without adding corner marks or notifications.",
  "选中记录后可查看路径、时间、状态，并执行同步、标记完成、Finder 显示或删除记录。": "When the record is selected, you can view the path, time, status, and perform synchronization, mark complete, finder display, or delete the record.",
  "通过 macOS FSEvents 捕获新增、修改、删除和重命名，变动会自动进入记录列表。": "Capture additions, modifications, deletions, and renames with macOS FSEvents, and the changes are automatically entered into the records list.",
  "重命名文件": "Rename File",
  "重新开启新手指引": "Reopen the guide",
  "频繁保存会重置等待时间，避免上传半成品。": "Frequent saving will reset the waiting time and avoid uploading semi-finished products.",
  "首次使用如何快速开始监控和同步？": "How do I quickly start monitoring and syncing for the first time?",
  "首次打开应用或在未登录状态下，主界面会显示微信登录二维码，扫码即可安全登录。": "When you open the app for the first time or when you are not logged in, the WeChat login QR code will be displayed on the main screen, and you can log in safely by scanning the code.",
  "首次打开应用，主界面会显示微信登录二维码。请使用微信扫码授权登录以绑定您的腾讯 IMA 账号。登录成功后，前往「设置 → 监控目录」点击添加您想监控的文件夹，并为该文件夹绑定对应的云端知识库，即可开始监控和同步文件。": "When you open the app for the first time, the WeChat login QR code will be displayed on the main screen. Please use WeChat scan code to authorize login to link your Tencent IMA account. After successfully logging in, go to \"Settings → Monitoring Directory\", click Add the folder you want to monitor, and bind the corresponding cloud knowledge base to the folder to start monitoring and syncing files.",
  "默认忽略规则": "Default ignore rule",
  "默认是手动同步。开启自动同步后，文件稳定 2 秒会自动上传到 IMA，适合持续写作或频繁保存的目录。": "The default is manual synchronization. After turning on automatic synchronization, the file will be automatically uploaded to IMA after 2 seconds of stability, suitable for continuous writing or frequently saved directories.",
  "默认过滤 .DS_Store、临时文件、系统目录、构建产物和常见缓存目录。": "Default filtering for .DS_Store, temporary files, system directories, build artifacts, and common cache directories.",
  "默认采用手动模式，点击单条“同步到 IMA”或首页“全部同步”后再上传。": "By default, the manual mode is used. Click the single \"Sync to IMA\" or \"Sync All\" on the homepage before uploading.",
  "：本项目为非盈利开源项目。上述捐赠行为完全基于您的自愿，所得款项仅用于补贴开发者维护项目所产生的时间、网络与服务器等基本支出，捐赠并非此软件的牟利手段，且不代表任何商业化销售或服务承诺。我们不对本软件的同步效率、腾讯云端稳定性或任何由同步冲突导致的数据异常承诺任何商业保障 or 赔偿。请知悉！": ": This is a non-profit open-source project. Donations are entirely voluntary and are used only to offset the maintainer's time, network, server, and basic project costs. Donations are not a commercial sale or service commitment. We do not provide commercial guarantees or compensation for sync efficiency, Tencent cloud stability, or data issues caused by sync conflicts. Please be aware.",
